{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "第四回\"铁血好男儿\"讲述铁中棠冒死营救师弟云铮的惊险历程。铁中棠趁乱纵火，以暗号\"并肩子，五福\"突破寒枫堡埋伏，将重伤昏迷的云铮带入荒山。冷一枫、司徒笑、盛大娘、白星武等人追击，白星武献计在水源设伏、搜索阴暗处。铁中棠识破埋伏，反其道走明路山路，却被司徒笑截住。铁中棠假意拜服，趁司徒笑得意忘形之际以肘拳踢腿暗算得手，抱起云铮再逃。误入暗林后，铁中棠以泥块诱敌、虚张声势等浅薄伎俩屡次骗过冷一枫与白星武。盛大娘以天女针射中铁中棠，盛存孝怜才手下留情。铁中棠被四名堡丁围困，寒枫堡持刀人赵奇刚认出铁中棠乃二十年前救命恩人之后，反戈击杀同伴相救。铁中棠力竭难行，恳求赵奇刚先带走云铮，自己留下断后。赵奇刚跪别铁血男儿，抱云铮消失晨雾中。铁中棠换尸伪装，仰卧装死骗过冷一枫、白星武搜索。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子身受重伤，小弟已尽可应付，白兄还是追敌去吧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你若肯说出他们所去之地，我便饶你一命！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "少爷早已存心死在这里，你难道不知道么？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗影中的埋伏者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "并肩子，五福！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "三弟！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们见我逃脱，不知又有何步骤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四下俱无敌踪，幸好还有个云家的后代被司徒兄擒住了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那厮何处去了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "逃走了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "司徒兄，那厮一个后生小辈，竟能在司徒笑兄手下逃脱，实令小弟有些不解！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "冷兄如此说话，难道还以为小弟是故意放他逃去的么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "幸好四面都有寒枫堡的埋伏，他反正逃不掉的！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "紧衣汉子",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "方才有两个少年走了，不知是什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们莫非都是死人，怎会放他们走的？你可知道他两人便是大旗门下！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "紧衣汉子",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "他们说出暗号，小的不敢拦阻……",
      "tone": "惶恐",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "那'五福'两字的暗语，本是司徒兄想出来的，却不知大旗弟子怎会知道？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要知道他们逃走的方向，不到天明，就可将他们捉回！",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么多人围住他们，都会让他们逃跑，再去追时，只怕更追不到了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不然，此刻那姓云的已连受我两次重创，是否能够活命，已难以预料，救他的人必定要为他疗伤，必定不会在荒山中停留。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "text": "他身上若带了伤药，又当怎地？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若有伤药，先得用清水洗涤伤口。深夜之中，在荒山里寻找他两人虽然不易，但我们只要寻着水源，在水源四下，布下埋伏，专等他们前来，还怕他们飞上天去么？",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错不错……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们狼狈逃命，必定不敢在正式山路上行走，你我只要专寻那阴暗之处搜索，再堵住四面出口，这样双管齐下，前后夹击，那二人除非胁生双翅，否则……嘿嘿，是再也逃不脱的了。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "白兄之计，果然大妙，看来司徒兄的'智囊'之名，要转赠白兄了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "智者千虑，必有一失，愚者千虑，必有一得，小弟一得之愚，怎及得上司徒兄！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事不宜迟，快！莫再多说了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好！我若是追踪之人，必定先要在阴暗之处搜索，我岂可落入别人算中？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三弟，天无绝人之路，只要今日能够逃脱，你的伤势必定还有救的。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗中人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "好一个狡黠的少年人！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "只可惜你的对手中，还有一个司徒笑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "你要怎样？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我早就知道你不会落入他们算中，必定要反道而行。此刻仍；已力竭，你伙伴更已重伤，无论要怎样，全都得看我的了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你还要等什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我与你无冤无仇，你为何要如此逼我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你我虽然无冤无仇，但谁教你身为大旗门的弟子？谁教你要拜在云老儿的门下？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "谁说我是大旗门弟子？我两人早已被大旗门逐出门墙，你杀了我们，又算得什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你花言巧语，骗得过别人，却骗不过我司徒笑！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "你若动手杀我，不但师出无名，反而更如了大旗门的心愿，日后他们说将出去，武林中人反要笑你为大旗门清除了门下弃徒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若不杀你又当如何？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "你今日若放了我，日后我便可带你去寻出大旗门的下落，那时不但你吐气扬眉，我也出了口冤气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你若要我罢手，除非你此刻便拜在我门下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "你说话可是真的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "合则两利，分则两败，我为何要骗你。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好！还有他呢？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "他此刻晕迷不醒，只有等他醒后……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "无耻的奴才，你……你以为我没有看到么？我生为大旗门人，死为大旗门鬼，你……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "这算做什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "他……他神智已有些不清了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你若要我信你，此刻就要先动手将他击毙，否则我还是难以相信。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "大旗门对你早已恩义断绝？你竟然还要效忠于他，你既然如此执迷不悟，我索性成全了你！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明明看他自这个方向逃出，怎的却又突然没有了影子？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "这厮虽然手快脚快，难道还会上天人地不成？怎会突地不见，只怕冷兄看错了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫怎会……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "小弟方才听得左面有响动之声，你我还是到那边看一看的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，只怕他们到那边去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我当你真有上天入地之能，原来你只不过是躲在树上而已。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你还想逃么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪里逃！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "着！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又中了这厮一计！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "这林中早已布下天罗地网，他逃得掉么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也明知这厮逃不掉的，恨就恨在这厮竟以一些顽童伎俩，骗过了老夫！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "这正是他狡滑之处，明知我们早已将这些顽童伎俩忘却，是以专用它来对付我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人留在世上，终是祸害。幸好他逃的那方向，正有一柄紫心剑、满袋天女针等着他哩！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "树上人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "小心些走，莫要绊倒了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好极了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "好什么？你见到老娘还好么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "text": "我苦苦寻找两位，此刻才找着，总算是苍天有眼，没有教我空走一趟。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "找老娘做什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "text": "两位看见了么？我辛辛苦苦地杀死了他，送到这里，两位总该赏我些什么才是，否则我当真有些冤枉了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你是什么人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "text": "哎哟，大娘你怎么不认得我了？想当年我小的时候，就……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "暗器，有人……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "少在老娘面前作怪，老娘不会上你的当的！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孝儿，莫放他逃了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_sheng_cun_xiao",
      "text": "长剑不斩徒手之人，你要杀就来杀吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "埋伏者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "点子往那边去了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "树上人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "树后大汉",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "哪里走？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "树上劲装大汉",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "这里也走不了的！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "罢了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "紧张什么？只管放大脚步过来便是，你铁家少爷索性成全了你们，决不动手！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "持刀汉子",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "姓铁的，你死到临头，还要逞凶么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死是什么滋味，你铁家少爷早想尝一尝了，只管放胆过来，看铁少爷可会皱一皱眉头！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 535
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "持刀大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "将这厮生擒，莫要伤了他性命，堡主还要审问于他，知道了吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "持刀人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慢着！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "被砍大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你疯了么！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友你……为什么……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "此时此刻，不是说话之处，铁公子快跟在下逃走……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "你不说清楚，我怎能随你而走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "二十年前，铁公子的先人铁老前辈，刀下留情，放过了一个少年赵奇刚的性命，那赵奇刚虽是个粗人，但二十年却从未将这救命大恩忘记，只可惜如今铁老前辈已仙去了。赵奇刚不能报大恩于铁老前辈生前，只有为铁老前辈的后人尽一份心力。前面不远，便是出林之路，公子你快伏在赵奇刚的背上，也好叫赵奇刚报恩于万一！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "赵兄，你……你……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "快，再迟就来不及了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 585
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "赵兄，你快将我怀中的兄弟抱起，逃命去吧，我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "公子你要怎样？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "我已不行了，你力不能背负我两人一齐逃走。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "为何不能，我拼命也要……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "那样只是枉送你我三人的性命而已。我留在这里，替你们挡住援兵，你们还有逃生之望！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "赵兄，你是条恩怨分明的热血男儿，怎能定要我做个不仁不义的人？我身受云家大恩，若将他留在这里，自己逃走，岂非变成了禽兽不如的畜牲！赵兄，你若不依我，铁中棠只有自杀一死！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "我已将这兄弟性命交托给你，你还不快走！只要你能救他一命，家父在九泉之下，也必定感激！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "快走，你救他如同救我，再不走我就……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "想不到世上竟有公子你这样的铁血男儿……好，依你！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 619
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三弟，永别了！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 625
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "赵兄，你何必如此？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "赵奇刚不是常会屈膝的男子，我这个头，乃是向一个顶天立地的义气汉子磕的，绝非只因你乃是铁老前辈的后人……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "小弟无话可说，只恨直到此时此刻，才认识赵兄这样的朋友！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 635
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "赵兄，我兄弟的性命，此刻全在赵兄手上，赵兄，你……你快去吧",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "铁公子……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "赵兄，别了！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "搜索者甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还找个什么，我看那厮满身重伤，八成是活不了的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 663
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "搜索者乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他死了还好，活着却惨了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "搜索者甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有时死了的确要比活着好些，我若是他，早就自杀了，一了百了，岂非又舒服，又痛快。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 669
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "堡丁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赵师傅，这里的暗卡，可有什么惊动么？堡主吩咐咱们，到这里……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 681
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又跑了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他身受数处重伤，怀里又抱着一人，我就不信他逃得掉，追！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 709
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "text": "且慢，你看这里！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "决不是的！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 717
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "text": "我这堡丁，虽然是个无用又无名的小卒，但他人已死了，白兄又何苦凌辱他的尸身！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 723
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "兄弟只是想看看这尸身是否他装死扮的，绝无……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "装死扮的……嘿嘿，白兄想得也未免太玄虚了些，他若有这种胆量……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好，我想起这无头尸身是谁了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 729,
      "line_end": 730
    }
